name: Number_digitsTest
description: Unit tests for the Number class's digits method with different count values.

test_cases.name: testDigitsWithPositiveCount
test_cases.description: Tests the digits method with a positive count, ensuring the result is a string of the specified length and contains only digits.

test_cases.name: testDigitsWithZeroCount
test_cases.description: Tests the digits method with a zero count, ensuring the result is an empty string.

test_cases.name: testDigitsWithNegativeCount
test_cases.description: Tests the digits method with a negative count, ensuring the result is an empty string after applying Math.max to ensure non-negative count.
